    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hyper Flux is a single-player speedrunning 3D platformer that puts you in control of a zero-gravity suit and a pair of orbs. Use your orbs to push and pull yourself through a broken world, where you speed through multiple planets before the world ends. Experience a comical story that starts with a bang, as you play as Elio, a tech-soldier who is tired of serving in the intergalactic war and after finally receiving his promised holiday, now has to complete his bucket list in this shattering world in just 24 hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a tech-soldier who uses a zero-gravity suit to navigate shattered planets in 3D using momentum. Don't forget to manage your fuel though..<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/90e1dc0a7e9d513c7a414ca611623ac4.poster.avif?t=1728902397\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/90e1dc0a7e9d513c7a414ca611623ac4.webm?t=1728902397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/90e1dc0a7e9d513c7a414ca611623ac4.mp4?t=1728902397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use push and pull orbs in zero-gravity to travel impossible distances super fast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/3c077ee38b128fef4f4e9028f154c8b2.poster.avif?t=1728902397\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/3c077ee38b128fef4f4e9028f154c8b2.webm?t=1728902397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/3c077ee38b128fef4f4e9028f154c8b2.mp4?t=1728902397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for the best time by utilizing your tools cleverly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/8cdefc6b05f6cd0e6e74312bdb2227dd.poster.avif?t=1728902397\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/8cdefc6b05f6cd0e6e74312bdb2227dd.webm?t=1728902397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/8cdefc6b05f6cd0e6e74312bdb2227dd.mp4?t=1728902397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect ingredients and upgrade your suit to achieve even faster times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/2e5f17453869c3d95c2a8ab0cfbe56c0.poster.avif?t=1728902397\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/2e5f17453869c3d95c2a8ab0cfbe56c0.webm?t=1728902397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260780/extras/2e5f17453869c3d95c2a8ab0cfbe56c0.mp4?t=1728902397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEMO CONTENT:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo will have limited amount of levels (mostly from world 1)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collectables will not be available for the most part.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards will be there in the demo but will not be carried over final game. The same also applies to your save files.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
